Returning a multi-epoch ephemeris
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

To return an ephemeris covering multiple epoch, simply append extra MJD values to the command:

.. code-block:: bash 
    
    rockfinder where ceres 57967.546 57970.146 57975.683 57982.256 57994.547

